item.title: Iraivi's courses for celebrating Motherhood
item.description: We provide the following services to best accompany you on your journey: Pregnancy nutrition Prenatal bonding Labor & birth Pre & postnatal fitness Breastfeeding Newborn care Postpartum care Lactation Counselling Expectant parents can attend personalized & group childbirth education classes.
